full_text: Pie BRA 2016/KER/44 IN THE HIGH COURT OF KERALA AT ERNAKULAM PRESENT: THE HONOURABLE MR. JUSTICE B.KEMAL PASHA MONDAY, THE 4TH DAY OF JANUARY 2016/14TH POUSHA, 1937 Crl.MC.No. 9 of 2016 () LPNO. 26/2014 OF JUDICIAL FIRST CLASS MAGISTRATE COURT -II, ERNAKULAM CRIME NO. 33/2007 OF ERNAKULAM CENTRAL POLICE STATION , ERNAKULAM PETITIONER/ACCUSED NO. 3: JEEVAN SABU, S/O SABU HARI, AGED 28 YEARS, KRISHNA KRIPA (H), GURUNAGAR, KOORKKANCHERRY P.O, THRISSUR-680 007 BY ADV. SRI.SANIL KUMAR RESPONDENT/COMPLAINANT: STATE OF KERALA, REPRESENTED BY THE PUBLIC PROSECUTOR, HIGH COURT OF KERALA, ERNAKULAM. BY PUBLIC PROSECUTOR SMT. MAYA THIS CRIMINAL MISC. CASE HAVING COME UP FOR ADMISSION ON 04-01-2016, THE COURT ON THE SAME DAY PASSED THE FOLLOWING: sts pea 2016/KER/44 B. KEMAL PASHA, J. Cril.M.C. No.9 of 2016 Dated this the 4" day of January, 2016 ORDER Heard learned counsel for the petitioner. 2. The court below is directed to dispose of the application seeking bail, if any filed by the petitioner, on his surrender before the court below within 10 days from today, preferably on the date of filing itself, provided advance notice on such application has been given to the Assistant Public Prosecutor also. Cri.M.C. is disposed of as above. Sd/- (B.KEMAL PASHA, JUDGE) aks/04/01 //! True Copy // PA to Judge
